Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是王留美  安排得很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢当
