Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  是和九条啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还好吗
