Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料中可没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being  是认真的
